"This allows a \"zero-copy\" when using intra-process communication during "
"data record or reply. This can significantly reduce CPU load during "
"recording or reply when dealing with high-bandwidth data streams and will "
"help to avoid data loss in the transport layer. It also provides the ability "
"to use YAML configuration files for ``rosbag2_transport::Player`` and "
"``rosbag2_transport::Recorder`` composable nodes."
